{"tid":920384,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"[Metalcore] While She Sleeps","createTime":"2018-11-28T19:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T12:40:24.000Z","uid":192257,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"f53d22ad6859878f33b3e0f253e23f976fcf58c5","tid":920384,"uid":192257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T19:10:35.000Z","msg":"While She Sleeps are an English metalcore band from Sheffield. Formed in 2006.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jx4kLrJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJx4kLrJ.png&h=dd0ef01a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由想當年既山海屯認識到佢地今日一直都非常喜歡<br />\n每個album都冇失望過<br />\n到之後浦吧再到music-zone每次聽都真係不得了<br />\n再追到去深圳  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且佢地好有心 仲係走tour時拍MV 我都有份架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />haha <br />\n<br />\n我好希望會有更多朋友仔認識佢地既音樂！<br />\n如果聽唔慣嘈既可以從佢地以幾首歌入手<br />\n睇埋歌詞會好過啲 因為幾有意思的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eH6tqXQNWUA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeH6tqXQNWUA&d=BEUgg9UfG23NtCXPAgLafwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=07f3c736\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eH6tqXQNWUA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1QH_1iN7ZmE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1QH_1iN7ZmE&d=BEUgg9UfG23NtCXPAgLafwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=6e5b29f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1QH_1iN7ZmE</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TM7DKXxAlH0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTM7DKXxAlH0&d=BEUgg9UfG23NtCXPAgLafwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=ad5cbb7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TM7DKXxAlH0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實好明白會覺得嘈既朋友仔 但希望你地唔好直接話我唔聽依啲 而損失左欣賞其他類型音樂既機會 仔細聽你會發現好full既底 rhythms<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同music flow好正架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n我1999完 希望你地會去睇佢地2019 一月份既live 啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔係打手係粉絲"},{"pid":"ea86f2dc7dbd08216eedbc80426070a078f50be2","tid":920384,"uid":66639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:00:14.000Z","msg":"冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d011e7b08a20e556c65f5aa4a3fc797c8b76b4","tid":920384,"uid":192257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea86f2dc7dbd08216eedbc80426070a078f50be2","tid":920384,"uid":66639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:00:14.000Z","msg":"冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T18:04:44.000Z","msg":"有人like已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4139bb178698c3f498ff4f21f0a7191d3009ec03","tid":920384,"uid":7119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T00:26:46.000Z","msg":"Where is your heart"},{"pid":"4323302d5fec6d7173a8db75ad2c52eb363aebc7","tid":920384,"uid":35637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T00:28:38.000Z","msg":"1月見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4403aafd5aaf7fd0a96917ac9340d32f13d5c9f","tid":920384,"uid":139829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T00:32:12.000Z","msg":"four walls in this prison"},{"pid":"0ef40ad33e915c864a67d56c601f4a57b73b2a74","tid":920384,"uid":108395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:29:42.000Z","msg":"一直覺得modern mind 係underrate"},{"pid":"417df0d928c17223d122e09d62817869d392db9f","tid":920384,"uid":61415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T11:41:55.000Z","msg":"有時覺得都係太pop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class